title: Evertrending Stories 4/21: California, Prince, Pete & Bas, Cruel Summer, Rusten Shesky, Vaccine Tax Incentives
itunes:title: Evertrending Stories 4/21: California, Prince, Pete & Bas, Cruel Summer, Rusten Shesky, Vaccine Tax Incentives
description:
On this Evertrending Stories Jack and Miles discuss California's low COVID rates, Prince's death day, Pete & Bas taking over UK hip hop, the teen drama "Cruel Summer", Rusten Shesky returning to work with no disciplinary action, and Biden's tax incentives for Covid vaccines.
